      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GUS THE GANGSTER (4) ran fourth on debut then quickly away and on speed throughout to score his maiden win by 0.8 lengths (25.64) at this track. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. TYPHOON PABLO (1) produced a moderate run last time when eighth at this track over 457m behind Salsa (26.24) in a Grade 6/MDN. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. GOLDSTAR GHOST (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (25.96) last time in a Grade 6/MDN at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. FORTUNE HEARTS (7) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
